next year for a sixth season as a crime-solving mystery writer on
``Murder, She Wrote.'' ``Angela Lansbury as Jessica Fletcher is one
of the most beloved characters on television,'' said Kim LeMasters,
president of CBS Entertainment. ``We are delighted that we will be
bringing her back for one more season.''
   The agreement was signed earlier this week with Universal
Television.
   The actress had said previously this would be her last season on
