<DATELINE>BOSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A stockbroker sought after allegedly disappearing
with millions of dollars of his client's funds was arrested today by
customs agents in Massena, N.Y., the U.S. Customs Service said.
   Walter F. Curran was trying to enter the United States from
Montreal after showing officers his Massachusetts drivers license. A
